WEBVTT

08:16.000 --> 08:17.160 line:80%
I found out that this man
didn't even tell me

08:17.160 --> 08:19.620 line:80%
about something as important
as getting married.

08:19.620 --> 08:21.550 line:80%
So I'm not sure anymore.

08:21.870 --> 08:23.130 line:80%
It happened suddenly.

08:23.540 --> 08:25.250 line:80%
It's not entirely his fault.
